# Admin — Licenses

### Search licenses (all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/licenses
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

###

### Search licenses by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/licenses?status=activated&take=20&skip=0
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

###

### Search licenses by product
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/licenses?product_id={{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

###

### Search licenses by batch
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/licenses?batch_id={{batchId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

###

### Read single license
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/licenses/{{licenseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

###

### Disable license
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/licenses/{{licenseId}}/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

###

### Enable license
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/licenses/{{licenseId}}/enable
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

###

### Revoke license
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/licenses/{{licenseId}}/revoke
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Payment refunded"
}

###

### Export licenses as CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/licenses/export.csv
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

###